text: Emily Saïdy de Jongh-Elhage (born 7 December 1946) is a former Curaçaoan politician. She was the 27th and last prime minister of the Netherlands Antilles from 2006 until its dissolution in 2010. ==Other websites== *Onze Kandidaten voor de Eilandsraad Verkiezingen *BBC Caribbean: Caribbean nationals to flee Lebanon Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of the Netherlands Antilles
